title: Coarse Hickory Branches
content:
Coarse Hickory Branches are an item passively gathered with the Woodcutter profession by lopping a hickory tree with tree loppers and a basket, requiring level 20 Woodcutter and 1 knowledge point. One set of branches is awarded for each hour spent gathering.

They can be purchased from Gwen's lumber store for US$4200 or sold for US$1600.
